                                                  SIMULATION OF
                         SES v4.1 file for testing the reading and conversion of forms.
                         Handles most forms - only ones missing are 6H (weird, causes a crash),
                         4A (this is an aero/thermo run not a fire run), 8D (train stopping points)
                         9K and 9L (flywheels) and 10 (stationary trains).
                         A case with tpopt=2; explicit speed-time, implicit heat gain calculation
                         Humidity displayed as kg/kg of dry air
                         Print option set to zero (designer oriented output)
